::Feline::

She came within range of the Cybertron fire.  she limpe up to the 
ship and hoped the scanners would pick her up.  She fell just before 
the ramp.  The hit to her leg was worse than she originally thought 
an made it painful to walk on it at all.  She got up and leaned 
against the ramp.  She waited to see if anyone would see her standing 
next to the ship on the visual scanners. If no one came, she would 
have to use her link.
